 1833|       |	 * the file scheme.
 1834|       |	 *
 1835|       |	 * XXX - however, it *also* means that
 1836|       |	 *
 1837|       |	 *    file://localhost/this/is/a/capture.pcap
 1838|       |	 *
 1839|       |	 * will be interpreted as a path, relative to the current
 1840|       |	 * directory, of "localhost/this/is/a/capture.pcap", not
 1841|       |	 * as an absolute path of "/this/is/a/capture.pcap".
 1842|       |	 */
