 1687|       |	 * you try pcap_activate()).  (If you don't allow programs to
 1688|       |	 * get as much information as possible about interfaces if you
 1689|       |	 * don't have permission to capture, you run the risk of users
 1690|       |	 * asking "why isn't it showing XXX" - or, worse, if you don't
 1691|       |	 * show interfaces *at all* if you don't have permission to
 1692|       |	 * capture on them, "why do no interfaces show up?" - when the
